总监杨悦卿以主播身份出现在直播间，解说牛排等食品。此前3月6日，杨悦卿在直播中提到，高合汽车将会通过直播间进行带货，且会把这些收入直接供到一线的售后的小伙伴，从而让车主们获得保障。 高合汽车申请破产重整！此前高管直播带货自救，老板丁磊也被多次限消 | 每经网"},"attached_info":"Cj8In4W78P37m6pyEAMaCTEwOTgwNTE0NSD8sNi1BjAAOCdACXIJNjYzODczNzYxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"90 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-5a11b6d9b639ad8ec2f879e040c70076_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"10_1723310121.858359","card_id":"Q_588399660","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":588399660,"title":"如何评价篮球比赛中快攻是easy ball这种说法？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/588399660","type":"question","created":1678292326,"answer_count":38,"follower_count":34,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[744,1538,4196,92889,118508],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4In4W78P37m6pyEAMaCDkzMDM3MTM4IObqoqAGMAA4IkAKcgk1ODgzOTk2NjB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"68 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-748886a5b4625544c94fe56a63b39486_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"11_1723310121.858673","card_id":"Q_45697482","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":45697482,"title":"FC上的游戏那么难，当年你们是什么心态和情绪通关的？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/45697482","type":"question","created":1462649568,"answer_count":29,"follower_count":36,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"